[Over the weekend I received a similar message from Valdir Roberto Welte,
Animal Health Officer (Disease Intelligence), Animal Health Service, FAO,
Rome, and Peter Roeder of the same organisation. I am glad to hear so
authoritatively that the situation in Northern Tanzania does not involve
CCPP. - Mod.MHJ
